dBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"❗各位新加入既會員注意⚠❗❗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點樣幫手:<br />\n- 有資源或金錢既善長，可以提供放映設備<br />\n- 有時間又經常發惡夢既義士手足，可以去落各區放映<br />\n- 經過見到有人放映，請邀請佢地，一齊搞大佢先可以遍地開花 <br />\n<br />\n需要啲咩物資?<br />\n- 流動投影機 / 電視<br />\n- Projector Screen (用電視就唔洗)<br />\n- 座枱<br />\n- 流動電源 <br />\n- Speaker <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊道搞放映會比較好? 幾點擺好?<br />\n- 連儂牆既位置最好﹐因為又唔怕落雨，自己人又多<br />\n- 時間上，建議選擇番人流比較多既時間，一黎人多冇咁易俾人搞，二黎比較有效率<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n播啲咩片? <br />\n📹<br />\n呢道有個 DataBase將啲片以字幕/主題/長度/媒體/發佈日期做分類，節省搵片時間，亦可以唔同地點播放唔同既片段 📹<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n✅影片下載教學: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2H1p3ix\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H1p3ix&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y98jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=8bd10b9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2H1p3ix</a> <br />\n<br />\n✅中英字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KpIbsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KpIbsA&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y98jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=a70bc772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2KpIbsA</a> <br />\n✅純中字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2YXU1lY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YXU1lY&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y98jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=8bd6f411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2YXU1lY</a><br />\n✅純英字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OQyTu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OQyTu6&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y98jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=5cdf2c37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OQyTu6</a><br />\n✅直播/冇字幕: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2yPNCdE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yPNCdE&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y98jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=222b4257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2yPNCdE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有啲咩法律問題?<br />\n<br />\nBy Law&rsquo;s Friend:<br />\n- 擺街放新聞應該要擺邊？<br />\n（Projector / Projecting Screen)<br />\nAnywhere that can allow reasonable passage of pedestrians after setting up<br />\n<br />\n- 使唔使申請?<br />\nLess than 30 ppl no need<br />\n<br />\n- 多過幾多人會變非法集會?<br />\nNot unlawful assembly if no action that make other people reasonably worry abt breach of peace. But could be unauthorised assembly if more than 30 ppl. <br />\n<br />\n- 遇到警察應該點處理？<br />\nIf the police wanna record ID number and name, they can <br />\nBut other than that, they shouldn&rsquo;t be able to do anything <br />\n<br />\n- 如到對家動手可以點?<br />\nThat&rsquo;s why it is better to have more ppl doing this together, and whenever there are quarrels, there should be ppl filming <br />\n<br />\n- 被檢控後可以點?<br />\nFind a lawyer once you get arrested, before the arrival of lawyer don&rsquo;t say anything to police apart from name and hkid no.It is not so soon that one is prosecuted"},{"pid":"70fb8f35cdbebe591ed5df33701ce181620bceff","tid":1460421,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:06:06.000Z","msg":"感謝"},{"pid":"b35b422630f35ba3e0a9d5c9fbc2696abfa30718","tid":1460421,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:17:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}